      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine 2013 BMW M3 (E92), a superlative example of the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8. This vehicle features a 6-speed manual transmission paired with a GKN variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal power delivery to the rear wheels. The engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, and the individual throttle bodies provide the razor-sharp response characteristic of this naturally aspirated masterpiece. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring the original EDC (Electronic Damping Control) and a structurally flawless carbon fiber roof. With no evidence of heat cycling on the plastics and a bone-dry undercarriage, this M3 represents the pinnacle of mechanical integrity and performance aesthetics.",
